Description.note: Dr. and Mrs. Phillip Lovell's beach house was designed and built by Rudolph Schindler in Newport Beach, California in 1926. Richard Neutra designed the landscaping for the beach house before winning the commission to build the Lovell's Los Angeles home, the Lovell Heath House, in 1927.
